data.description: This 3 bedroom 2 bath house has had all the big updates done recently!  A new roof was installed this year along with leaf guards on the guttering and new insulation installed by Terminex. The HVAC was newly installed in 2018. All new windows from Window World and a tankless gas water heater were installed approximately 5 years ago. Never be without power with the Generac Centurion generator that powers the entire house and comes on and shuts off automatically. The primary suite has a nice size walk in closet and both bathrooms have walk in showers. There is a screened in back porch and the back yard is fully fenced. This one is low maintenance and conveniently located. Call your favorite REALTOR® and schedule a private tour today!
